videos.headline: McElwain says this year's Bama team is Saban's best
videos.description: Florida coach Jim McElwain has high praise for this year's Alabama football team that beat the Gators in the SEC title game.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Presser (McElwain says this year's Bama team is best Saban's ever had) 2016/12/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Kiffin deflects head coaching talk after win
videos.description: Lane Kiffin doesn't have much interest in talking about anything other than how Alabama played against Florida after the Crimson Tide's win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Kiffin deflects head coaching talk after win) 2016/12/03

videos.headline: Saban proud of Bama for significant accomplishments
videos.description: Nick Saban talks about how proud he is of Alabama for completing an undefeated regular season and winning three straight SEC titles.
